cs.IR, cs.HC, cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.SI 

The paper is about an online access panel for evaluating Interactive Information Retrieval (IIR) systems. This topic falls under the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of natural language processing techniques (cs.CL) and the potential for cybersecurity concerns (cs.CY) in the implementation of the online access panel. Finally, the paper discusses the potential for collaboration with other researchers in the field of IIR, which could fall under the Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-category.
